        {
            "title": "特朗普：周一將與俄羅斯總統普京通電話  再與澤連斯基通話",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"路透社\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/6c65c1fcfa197e11624d58cf4006956f/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250517/_2025051723163659935.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">路透社</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>美國總統特朗普在社交平台表示，於當地時間週一上午10點與俄羅斯總統普京通電話。他指，會議的主題將是停止這場平均每週造成5000多名俄羅斯和烏克蘭士兵死亡的「大屠殺」以及貿易。\n\n</p>\n<p>隨後特朗普將與澤連斯基通話，並與澤連斯基一起和北約各成員國通話。他表示，希望這將是富有成效的一天，達成停火。\n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/2069471/即時-國際-特朗普-周一將與俄羅斯總統普京通電話-再與澤連斯基通話",
            "pub_date": "2025-05-17 23:21:23",
            "source": "stheadline",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "鳳德道爆水管｜多條巴士路線改道 水務署安排水車支援 多人排隊取水",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/992535f1c1b0f5f0de350e9049ce5a95/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250517/_2025051722524262545.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\"></figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>鑽石山鳳德道及蒲崗村道交界今日（17日）爆水管，涉及一條直徑450毫米的食水管需要緊急維修，鳳德邨一帶的食水供應受到影響。\n\n</p>\n<p>水務署立刻安排水車及水箱，為受影響的居民及商戶提供臨時食水供應，又已聯絡當區區議員及關愛隊以提供適切協助。\n\n</p>\n<p>至晚上，多名居民帶同水桶到水車取水，秩序大致良好。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4254589/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"水務署立刻安排水車及水箱，為受影響的居民及商戶提供臨時食水供應。黃文威攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/b4f5885b61fb940c91570f8a072b12fe/2025-05/KakaoTalk_20250517_220432810_08.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        水務署立刻安排水車及水箱，為受影響的居民及商戶提供臨時食水供應。黃文威攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4254590/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"名居民帶同水桶到水車取水，秩序大致良好。黃文威攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/27a2a620aaa35f7e40e631578fd14d01/2025-05/KakaoTalk_20250517_220432810_07.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        名居民帶同水桶到水車取水，秩序大致良好。黃文威攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4254591/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"名居民帶同水桶到水車取水，秩序大致良好。黃文威攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/fed1bc43aa5630f0208bb7a64fb96f22/2025-05/KakaoTalk_20250517_220432810_06.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        名居民帶同水桶到水車取水，秩序大致良好。黃文威攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4254592/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"名居民帶同水桶到水車取水，秩序大致良好。黃文威攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/05c2be88210e5431b82d7fb91b488333/2025-05/KakaoTalk_20250517_220432810_03.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        名居民帶同水桶到水車取水，秩序大致良好。黃文威攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4254593/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"名居民帶同水桶到水車取水，秩序大致良好。黃文威攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/7252d7acdd4fc8d2cace65b31e56eaf4/2025-05/KakaoTalk_20250517_220432810_02.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        名居民帶同水桶到水車取水，秩序大致良好。黃文威攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4254594/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"名居民帶同水桶到水車取水，秩序大致良好。黃文威攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/a6675b47c29a2021e2346fa50f6ac9b1/2025-05/KakaoTalk_20250517_220432810_01.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        名居民帶同水桶到水車取水，秩序大致良好。黃文威攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<p><strong>相關新聞：<a href=\"https://www.stheadline.com/breaking-news/3456446/\">鑽石山鳳德道爆食水管 黃泥水淹浸行車線 大面積路陷</a></strong>\n</p>\n<p>事件發生於晚上7時10分，鑽石山鳳德道及蒲崗村道交界爆水管，大量黃泥水湧出，道路出現巨大裂縫，整條馬路凹凸不平，駛近車輛需要停下及打死火燈，途人亦要涉水而行。\n\n</p>\n<p>運輸署表示，因水管爆裂，鳳德道(來回方向)介乎蒲崗村道與鳳德邨通道之間的全線現已封閉。受影響九巴第3B、10、11、11C、61X、75X、82X、85、91M及671號線須改道⾏駛。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4254436/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"鳳德道及蒲崗村道交界有水管爆裂。黃文威攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/ce8610201d7bf213e3a69abfa03610c7/2025-05/KakaoTalk_20250517_201210435_12.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        鳳德道及蒲崗村道交界有水管爆裂。黃文威攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<p> \n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4254437/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"鳳德道及蒲崗村道交界有水管爆裂。黃文威攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/b7cd5c4ff1f1d3e524c16e31f8dce0d5/2025-05/KakaoTalk_20250517_201210435_11.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        鳳德道及蒲崗村道交界有水管爆裂。黃文威攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4254438/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"鳳德道及蒲崗村道交界有水管爆裂。黃文威攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/51ce40a6552f8878c2554047077fb9e8/2025-05/KakaoTalk_20250517_201210435_10.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        鳳德道及蒲崗村道交界有水管爆裂。黃文威攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4254439/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"鳳德道及蒲崗村道交界有水管爆裂。黃文威攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/1b5221d6a078aaed820eab71621b939a/2025-05/KakaoTalk_20250517_201210435_09.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        鳳德道及蒲崗村道交界有水管爆裂。黃文威攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4254440/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"鳳德道及蒲崗村道交界有水管爆裂。黃文威攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/2d9c2e858b3e71f1fdbc6784b799b836/2025-05/KakaoTalk_20250517_201210435_05.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        鳳德道及蒲崗村道交界有水管爆裂。黃文威攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4254441/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"鳳德道及蒲崗村道交界有水管爆裂。黃文威攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/5ff8255905aaec7a25266ab462f5657b/2025-05/KakaoTalk_20250517_201210435_01.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        鳳德道及蒲崗村道交界有水管爆裂。黃文威攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
