            "title": "黃大仙Tesla警車相撞 兩車車身損毀無人傷",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/3f8655e23ee667f96b98f5157e0f1201/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250517/_2025051721110187908.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\"></figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>今日（17日）傍晚6時許，一輛警車沿黃大仙東頭村道行駛，至黃大仙下邨龍慧樓對開與一輛Tesla私家車發生相撞，兩車車身輕微損毀，事件中無人受傷。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4254497/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"一輛警車在黃大仙下邨龍慧樓對開與一輛Tesla私家車發生相撞。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/937df07bacd8c0faa77ee8615216b875/2025-05/WhatsApp_Image_2025-05-17_at_20_27_13.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        一輛警車在黃大仙下邨龍慧樓對開與一輛Tesla私家車發生相撞。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
