        {
            "title": "新蒲崗采頤花園女子倒斃屋內 被大量雜物壓住僅現手臂 胞弟上門揭發",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/fa01a47f26f37a1880b7c86b6bd03a5a/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250517/_2025051721240882426.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\"></figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>今日（17日）晚上8時許，警方接獲一名男子報案，指與胞姐失聯兩日，遂下午前往新蒲崗采頤花園探訪了解，惟打開房門時，發現對方被大量雜物壓住掩埋，只露出一截手臂，奄奄一息。消防到場協助救出女子，證實她當場不治，警方正調查事件。\n\n</p>\n<p>據了解，上址單位放滿大量雜物，非常凌亂。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4254503/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"現場為新蒲崗采頤花園。黃文威攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/d0892f574038e0c94b348a3b2d9ab12c/2025-05/KakaoTalk_20250517_211038353_01.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        現場為新蒲崗采頤花園。黃文威攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4254504/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"女子當場證實不治。黃文威攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/e7435a020ca5f0d108f40bae79e7194f/2025-05/KakaoTalk_20250517_211038353.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        女子當場證實不治。黃文威攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4254505/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"警方正調查事件。黃文威攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/d3a617f742ec1663375921e9d4e2fd20/2025-05/KakaoTalk_20250517_211722297.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        警方正調查事件。黃文威攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4254506/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"警方上門調查事件。黃文威攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/36c3e417e452a452fd9a5f583c734bd9/2025-05/KakaoTalk_20250517_211209575_02.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        警方上門調查事件。黃文威攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4254507/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"警方上門調查事件。黃文威攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/a051976b6ee76ef12c5cca1d1786af9a/2025-05/KakaoTalk_20250517_211209575.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item_